      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
    </div>

h3 Fluid buttons
p.-text Button groups can be expanded to fill the parent space by applying the class <code>-fluid</code>.
h4 Horizontal
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .m-btnGroup.-fluid(style="width:100%")
      button(class=`a-btn`) Button
      button(class=`a-btn`) Button
      button(class=`a-btn`) Button
  :code(lang='html')
    <div class="m-btnGroup -fluid">
      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
    </div>

