      <button class="a-btn -align--left">Button</button>
      <button class="a-btn">Button</button>
      <button class="a-btn -align--right">Button</button>
    </div>

h4 Disable Fluidity
p.-text
  | To disable the fluidity of a specific button in a fluid button group, apply the class <code>-notFluid</code> to the button.

.example.-mb--3
